channel.title: Need Autospawn Help
channel.description: I read this guide on how to add shops (Yes, i'm a beginner), and the guide says to open Autospawn.cfg. When i go to open it, i get this odd window... and it doesnt let me into the Autospawn.cfg. Is there anyway i can get it open to edit, add, and delete shops?
